title: Affair-Proof Your Marriage, Part 9
itunes:author: John Fuller & Greg Smalley
itunes:summary: It can be easy to fall into the trap of feeling like certain parts of your marriage aren't your job. John and Greg discuss how hectic seasons of life bring extra responsibilities. Featuring Dave Carder.
